Notebook[{

Cell[CellGroupData[{
Cell["\<\
Studying the  evolution of density distribution in a discrete graph
\
\>", "Title",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.770055572438499*^9, 3.7700555729498453`*^9}, {
  3.770055604008165*^9, 3.7700556066618843`*^9}, {3.832335945198794*^9, 
  3.832335946914747*^9}, {3.898207319104958*^9, 3.898207380829995*^9}, {
  3.898227445852058*^9, 
  3.898227449067554*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"d40af42c-7cc4-4933-a50e-\
e14799516fe8"],

Cell["Ananya Mukherjee", "Author",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.549624168509506*^9, 3.549624171985794*^9}, {
  3.549624508772977*^9, 3.549624510775043*^9}, {3.5498187159613867`*^9, 
  3.5498187170087957`*^9}, {3.549819049020514*^9, 3.5498190533440437`*^9}, {
  3.77005561844785*^9, 3.7700556489651537`*^9}, {3.832335949309461*^9, 
  3.832335952432062*^9}, {3.8982073580173473`*^9, 
  3.898207361064062*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"e9f35d69-5d99-452b-8633-\
77abb35d8797"],

Cell["University of Massachusetts, Lowell", "Affiliation",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.802186209582007*^9, 3.802186214327465*^9}, {
  3.832335954006332*^9, 3.8323359557765293`*^9}, {3.898207363265383*^9, 
  3.898207372156884*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f6dca342-e6d9-43a4-a93a-\
eba6b9c09452"],

Cell["\<\
Abstract: In this project we are studying the clustering of mass on a \
discrete graph model under the influence of gravity. This simple model could \
be used as a first step to study the formation of the Large Scale structure \
in the Universe, with the underlying manifold being described by discrete \
hypergraph. \
\>", "Abstract",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.802186680026499*^9, 3.802186711462531*^9}, {
  3.8323359571935577`*^9, 3.832335959648123*^9}, {3.833031302355076*^9, 
  3.833031316081359*^9}, {3.833031479749832*^9, 3.833031483591234*^9}, {
  3.898225939823072*^9, 3.898226098126471*^9}, {3.898226158327895*^9, 
  3.8982261653086348`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"25a58851-fbdc-41a2-9c75-\
d65abe727288"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[" Introduction", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.802186221820878*^9, 3.8021862228082314`*^9}, {
   3.83233589828449*^9, 3.832335898684196*^9}, {3.8323359631232023`*^9, 
   3.832335974308188*^9}, {3.8982072543754807`*^9, 3.898207258115716*^9}, 
   3.8982261168588133`*^9},ExpressionUUID->"cb1f792a-7f96-4a8b-96ce-\
90911c46898b"],

Cell[TextData[{
 " At an enormous scale (~ 100Mpc), bigger than the length scale of \
individual galaxies the Universe displays a web-like structure, with galaxies \
bounded gravitationally forming a filament like structure of galaxy clusters, \
 punctured by empty spaces (void) with very few galaxies inside. All these \
massive structures in the Universe  is known as the Large Scale structure \
(LSS) of the spacetime. The gravitational interaction between them is the key \
factor that determines the evolution of the Universe. Over the course of time \
the galaxies are drifting toward each other forming a cluster and \
supercluster subsequently. It is believed that the Milky way is merging \
toward the Virgo cluster, which will itself merge with the Centaurus and \
Shapley superclusters which make up the Great Attractor.\nThese LSS can be a \
very important tool to understand the fundamental forces of the nature. By \
studying the clustering properties of matter it is possible to fathom the \
underlying theory of gravity in play. Another salient feature of the  LSS is, \
 we can also extract the information about dark energy. The dark energy is \
postulated to be the source of the cosmic accelerated expansion, where we can \
observe that the Universe is expanding rapidly instead of the immense \
gravitational pull that should slow it down. By observing  the rate of \
clustering we can optimize the parameter space of the theoretical models of \
dark energy.  Thus from the point of view of Cosmology it is extremely \
important to understand the formation mechanism of these structure. The \
mathematical tool used to study the LSS is the theory of general relativity, \
where the space-time manifold is described by a metric and curvature tensors.\
\n     \n  In",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontSlant->"Italic"],
 "the Wolfram model introduced the a class of minimal, structureless model, \
which proved to be very much relevant to study the fundamental properties of \
the nature.",
 StyleBox[" ",
  FontSlant->"Italic",
  FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0, 1]],
 "In this model the space could be represented by a collection of discreet \
points and physical laws can be represented by the transformation rules \
defined on the graph. A more general approach to model the space by a \
hypergraph has been proposed in recent years.",
 StyleBox["  ",
  FontSlant->"Italic",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["The conformal structure of the spacetime is preserved by causal \
graphs. The notion of the curvature of the spacetime and dimension are \
emergent in the causal structure of the graph. The discrete form of the \
Einstein\[CloseCurlyQuote]s field equation can be obtained by applying the \
set of constraints on the discrete Ricci tensor.",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["\n",
  FontSlant->"Italic",
  FontColor->RGBColor[0, 0, 1]],
 "\nIn this project we are focussing on developing a framework for the \
dynamics under gravitational interaction on a connected graph, and study how \
the mass density would be flowing among vertices. The next section we \
describe the simple model we have used in the study and the following section \
will give a walk-through the Mathematica algorithm. "
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8021862859717093`*^9, 3.8021862866993*^9}, {
   3.802186780928506*^9, 3.802186861789569*^9}, {3.832335906349555*^9, 
   3.832335909229568*^9}, {3.832336112805627*^9, 3.832336113421673*^9}, 
   3.833031536056086*^9, {3.83303157648634*^9, 3.8330315963449383`*^9}, {
   3.898207268166419*^9, 
   3.898207272440919*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"8531d6de-a8f6-4f3c-a75f-\
3fac0e7e31d6"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Theoretical background", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8323359221544037`*^9, 3.83233592410432*^9}, {
  3.832335977658493*^9, 3.8323359780031157`*^9}, {3.898207282759328*^9, 
  3.898207286490169*^9}, {3.8982073856163807`*^9, 
  3.898207397820385*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"cd066514-9339-4163-a1c0-\
8e8e52851eb4"],

Cell[TextData[{
 StyleBox["To simulate the formation of mass clustering, we  start with a \
simple grid graph of ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["N",
  FontSlant->"Italic",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["  particles, and assign a mass density  on each of its vertices. \
The mass density on each vertex is interacting with every other vertex in the \
graph. Their gravitational interaction dictates the dynamical evolution of \
this system of masses. \nWe start with 100 vertices arranged in a 10X10 grid \
graph. Using a random number generator we are assigning mass density to each \
of its vertices. \nAssuming gravity to be the only force acting in the \
system, the pairwise gravitational force between ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox["i-j",
  FontSlant->"Italic",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 StyleBox[" th pair is given by, ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["F", "ij"], "=", 
    RowBox[{"G", 
     FractionBox[
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["m", "1"], 
       SubscriptBox["m", "2"]}], 
      SuperscriptBox[
       SubscriptBox["r", "ij"], "2"]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "074ed4d1-ea6b-4f67-a0aa-313b453e2927"],
 StyleBox[", where G = ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{"6.674", 
    SuperscriptBox["X10", 
     RowBox[{"-", "11"}]], " ", 
    RowBox[{"N", ".", 
     SuperscriptBox["m", "2"], ".", 
     SuperscriptBox["kg", "2"]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "6533761b-3eb6-4686-a56a-b9a756ed5d55"],
 StyleBox[",Newton\[CloseCurlyQuote]s gravitational constant. \nThe \
gravitational potential at j-th particle due to i-th particle is, ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["U", "ij"], "=", 
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"-", "G"}], 
     FractionBox[
      SubscriptBox["m", "j"], 
      SubscriptBox["r", "ij"]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "ce8c7b58-f21e-4876-983a-84472c70cb44"],
 StyleBox[". \nIn the mass transfer scheme we have defined a parameter, \
\[ScriptF], which will control the amount of mass transfer on each step. The \
weight defined as,  ",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]],
 Cell[BoxData[
  FormBox[
   RowBox[{
    SubscriptBox["\[ScriptW]", "j"], "=", 
    RowBox[{"\[ScriptF]", " ", 
     SubscriptBox["m", "j"], 
     FractionBox[
      SubscriptBox["U", "ij"], 
      RowBox[{
       SubscriptBox["\[Sum]", 
        RowBox[{"i", ",", "j"}]], 
       SubscriptBox["U", "ij"]}]]}]}], TraditionalForm]],ExpressionUUID->
  "e00f72ad-0ad5-4e05-8acd-ee638d72ef67"],
 StyleBox[". \n",
  FontColor->GrayLevel[0]]
}], "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8021862859717093`*^9, 3.8021862866993*^9}, {
   3.802186780928506*^9, 3.802186861789569*^9}, {3.832335906349555*^9, 
   3.832335909229568*^9}, 3.83303154442404*^9, {3.898207405100953*^9, 
   3.8982074179379387`*^9}, {3.898207562439248*^9, 3.8982076573468027`*^9}, {
   3.898223817576024*^9, 
   3.898223850560657*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"58967191-164e-42fa-b7a7-\
94b792bbd42d"]
}, Open  ]],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Mathematica syntax", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.802186221820878*^9, 3.8021862228082314`*^9}, {
  3.832335902664353*^9, 3.832335903014779*^9}, {3.83233597998449*^9, 
  3.832335980318049*^9}, {3.898207426277215*^9, 
  3.898207433100266*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"781fb6d7-3a5d-4184-9892-\
bbf7f7c4652e"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"fconstant", "=", "0.01"}], ";"}]], "Input",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.898182142741894*^9, 3.898182146890277*^9}, {
   3.898200593442211*^9, 3.898200612670957*^9}, 3.8982094541163607`*^9},
 CellLabel->"In[1]:=",ExpressionUUID->"046e2fd0-a6e8-464e-9e66-ccc0dc967007"],

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{
  RowBox[{"(*", 
   RowBox[{
   "Calculation", " ", "of", " ", "gravitational", " ", "potential", " ", 
    "between", " ", "all", " ", "pair", " ", "of", " ", "vertices"}], "*)"}], 
  "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"Uijgrid", "[", 
     RowBox[{"masses_", ",", "gridgraph_", ",", "i_", ",", " ", "j_"}], "]"}],
     " ", ":=", " ", 
    RowBox[{"Piecewise", "[", 
     RowBox[{"{", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"{", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"-", 
           RowBox[{"masses", "[", 
            RowBox[{"[", "j", "]"}], "]"}]}], "/", 
          RowBox[{"GraphDistance", "[", 
           RowBox[{"gridgraph", ",", " ", "i", ",", " ", "j"}], "]"}]}], " ", 
         ",", 
         RowBox[{"i", " ", "=!=", " ", "j"}]}], "}"}], ",", 
       RowBox[{"{", 
        RowBox[{"0", ",", " ", 
         RowBox[{"i", " ", "===", " ", "j"}]}], "}"}]}], "}"}], "]"}]}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{"(*", 
    RowBox[{
    "gives", " ", "the", " ", "list", " ", "of", " ", "weighted", " ", "mass",
      " ", "that", " ", "should", " ", "be", " ", "transferred"}], " ", 
    "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"weightedMass", "[", 
      RowBox[{"potentialmMax_", ",", "masses_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"fconstant", "*", 
        RowBox[{"masses", "[", 
         RowBox[{"[", "#", "]"}], "]"}], "*", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"potentialmMax", "[", 
          RowBox[{"[", "#", "]"}], "]"}], "/", 
         RowBox[{"Total", "[", "potentialmMax", "]"}]}]}], "&"}], "/@", 
      RowBox[{"Range", "[", 
       RowBox[{"Length", "[", "masses", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], ";"}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{"(*", 
    RowBox[{
    "gives", " ", "the", " ", "amount", " ", "of", " ", "mass", " ", "that", 
     " ", "should", " ", "be", " ", "transferred", " ", "from", " ", "the", 
     " ", "given", " ", "vertices"}], "*)"}], "\n", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"massTransfer", "[", 
      RowBox[{"potentialmMax_", ",", "masses_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
     RowBox[{"AssociationThread", "[", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"Range", "[", 
        RowBox[{"Length", "[", "masses", "]"}], "]"}], "\[Rule]", 
       RowBox[{"weightedMass", "[", 
        RowBox[{"potentialmMax", ",", "masses"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";"}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
    RowBox[{
    "calculates", " ", "the", " ", "position", " ", "of", " ", "biggest", " ",
      "mass"}], "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{
     RowBox[{"maxV", "[", "masses_", "]"}], ":=", 
     RowBox[{"First", "@", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"Position", "[", 
         RowBox[{"masses", ",", 
          RowBox[{"Max", "[", "masses", "]"}]}], "]"}], "[", 
        RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}], "[", 
       RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], ";"}], " ", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   
   RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
    RowBox[{
    "gives", " ", "the", " ", "amount", " ", "of", " ", "mass", " ", "to", 
     " ", "be", " ", "transferred", " ", "from", " ", "each", " ", 
     "vertices"}], "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"massQueuefn", "[", 
     RowBox[{"masses_", ",", "gridgraph_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"potentialmMax", " ", "=", " ", 
       RowBox[{"Table", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Uijgrid", "[", 
          RowBox[{"masses", ",", "gridgraph", ",", 
           RowBox[{"maxV", "[", "masses", "]"}], ",", "j"}], "]"}], ",", 
         RowBox[{"{", 
          RowBox[{"j", ",", " ", "1", ",", 
           RowBox[{"Length", "[", "masses", "]"}]}], "}"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
       RowBox[{"calculates", " ", "the", " ", "potential"}], "*)"}], 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"massTransfer", "[", 
       RowBox[{"potentialmMax", ",", "masses"}], "]"}]}], "}"}]}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
    RowBox[{
    "add", " ", "the", " ", "largest", " ", "mass", " ", "to", " ", 
     "updatedMasses", " ", "and", " ", "set", " ", "it", " ", "to", " ", 
     "zero", " ", "in", " ", "masses"}], "*)"}], "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"updateMasses", "[", 
     RowBox[{"masses_", ",", "massQueue_", ",", "updatedMasses_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"posmaxV", " ", "=", 
       RowBox[{"maxV", "[", "masses", "]"}]}], ";", 
      RowBox[{"rawmasses", "=", 
       RowBox[{"KeyValueMap", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{
          RowBox[{"{", 
           RowBox[{"#", ",", 
            RowBox[{
             RowBox[{"masses", "[", "#", "]"}], "-", 
             RowBox[{"massQueue", "[", "#", "]"}]}]}], "}"}], "&"}], ",", 
         "masses"}], "]"}]}], ";", " ", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"masses1", "=", 
       RowBox[{"AssociationThread", "[", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"rawmasses", "[", 
          RowBox[{"[", 
           RowBox[{";;", ",", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}], ",", 
         RowBox[{"rawmasses", "[", 
          RowBox[{"[", 
           RowBox[{";;", ",", "2"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], "]"}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"masses1", "[", 
        RowBox[{"[", "posmaxV", "]"}], "]"}], "=", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"masses1", "[", 
         RowBox[{"[", "posmaxV", "]"}], "]"}], "+", 
        RowBox[{"Total", "[", 
         RowBox[{"Values", "[", 
          RowBox[{"Normal", "[", "massQueue", "]"}], "]"}], "]"}]}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"updatedMasses1", "=", 
       RowBox[{"Append", "[", 
        RowBox[{"updatedMasses", ",", 
         RowBox[{"posmaxV", "->", 
          RowBox[{"masses1", "[", 
           RowBox[{"[", "posmaxV", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], "]"}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{
       RowBox[{"masses1", "[", 
        RowBox[{"[", "posmaxV", "]"}], "]"}], "=", "0"}], ";", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
       RowBox[{"masses1", ",", "updatedMasses1"}], "}"}]}], "}"}]}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"MassTransferIteration", "[", 
     RowBox[{"masses_", ",", "gridgraph_"}], "]"}], ":=", 
    RowBox[{"{", 
     RowBox[{
      RowBox[{"massQueue", "=", 
       RowBox[{"First", "@", 
        RowBox[{"massQueuefn", "[", 
         RowBox[{"masses", ",", "gridgraph"}], "]"}]}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"updatedMasses", "=", 
       RowBox[{"<|", "|>"}]}], ";", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"masses1", "=", "masses"}], ";", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"While", "[", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"Length", "[", "updatedMasses", "]"}], "<", 
         RowBox[{"(", 
          RowBox[{"Length", "[", "masses1", "]"}], ")"}]}], ",", 
        "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
        RowBox[{
         RowBox[{"masslist", "=", 
          RowBox[{"updateMasses", "[", 
           RowBox[{"masses1", ",", "massQueue", ",", "updatedMasses"}], 
           "]"}]}], ";", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
         RowBox[{"masses1", "=", 
          RowBox[{"masslist", "[", 
           RowBox[{"[", 
            RowBox[{"1", ",", "1"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], ";", 
         RowBox[{"updatedMasses", "=", 
          RowBox[{"masslist", "[", 
           RowBox[{"[", 
            RowBox[{"1", ",", "2"}], "]"}], "]"}]}], ";", 
         "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
         RowBox[{"If", "[", 
          RowBox[{
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"Count", "[", 
             RowBox[{"masses1", ",", 
              RowBox[{"x_", "/;", 
               RowBox[{"x", "!=", "0"}]}]}], "]"}], "==", "1"}], ",", 
           RowBox[{
            RowBox[{"nonzeroindex", " ", "=", " ", 
             RowBox[{"First", "@", 
              RowBox[{
               RowBox[{"Position", "[", 
                RowBox[{
                 RowBox[{"Values", "[", "masses1", "]"}], ",", 
                 RowBox[{"_", "?", 
                  RowBox[{"(", 
                   RowBox[{
                    RowBox[{"#", "!=", "0"}], "&"}], ")"}]}]}], "]"}], "[", 
               RowBox[{"[", "1", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], ";", 
            RowBox[{"AppendTo", "[", 
             RowBox[{"updatedMasses", ",", 
              RowBox[{"nonzeroindex", "->", 
               RowBox[{"masses1", "[", 
                RowBox[{"[", "nonzeroindex", "]"}], "]"}]}]}], "]"}], ";", 
            RowBox[{"Break", "[", "]"}]}]}], "]"}], ";", 
         "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
         RowBox[{"massQueue", "=", 
          RowBox[{"First", "@", 
           RowBox[{"massQueuefn", "[", 
            RowBox[{"masses1", ",", "gridgraph"}], "]"}]}]}], ";"}]}], 
       "\[IndentingNewLine]", "]"}], ";", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
      RowBox[{"masses1", "=", 
       RowBox[{"KeySort", "[", "updatedMasses", "]"}]}], ";", 
      "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", "masses1"}], "}"}]}], 
   "\[IndentingNewLine]", "\[IndentingNewLine]", 
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"makeGrid", "[", "masses_", "]"}], ":=", 
    RowBox[{"Graph", "[", 
     RowBox[{"grid", ",", " ", 
      RowBox[{"VertexWeight", " ", "->", " ", 
       RowBox[{"Normal", "[", "masses", "]"}]}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"(*", " ", 
       RowBox[{
        RowBox[{"VertexLabels", " ", "->", " ", "Automatic"}], ","}], "*)"}], 
      " ", 
      RowBox[{"VertexSize", " ", "->", " ", 
       RowBox[{"Normal", "[", "masses", "]"}]}], ",", 
      RowBox[{"EdgeStyle", "\[Rule]", "Dashed"}]}], "]"}], " "}]}]}]], "Input",\

 CellChangeTimes->{{3.8981854749111557`*^9, 3.8981854980634212`*^9}, {
  3.8981855349646893`*^9, 3.898185556513929*^9}, {3.89818566531574*^9, 
  3.898185710764744*^9}, {3.898185743560905*^9, 3.89818579601019*^9}, {
  3.89818585651532*^9, 3.898185860504858*^9}, {3.898185905066752*^9, 
  3.898185907154255*^9}, {3.898185996378172*^9, 3.898185996704172*^9}, {
  3.898186027763853*^9, 3.898186027851138*^9}, {3.898187269342265*^9, 
  3.8981873112264423`*^9}, {3.8981886851481743`*^9, 3.8981887536787148`*^9}, {
  3.898196058842279*^9, 3.898196069437027*^9}, {3.898208299745771*^9, 
  3.898208308215027*^9}, {3.898208346546349*^9, 3.898208352618845*^9}, {
  3.898212528206208*^9, 3.898212531923435*^9}, {3.8982239296145763`*^9, 
  3.898223930528554*^9}},
 CellLabel->"In[27]:=",ExpressionUUID->"456be17d-5b0b-4101-8ce1-8a45f8ae6a81"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData[
 RowBox[{" ", 
  RowBox[{
   RowBox[{
    RowBox[{"i", "=", "10"}], ";", 
    RowBox[{"grid", " ", "=", " ", 
     RowBox[{"GridGraph", "[", 
      RowBox[{"{", 
